description:
8.62 asupercut
Cut super frequencies.

The filter accepts the following options:
name: asupercut

options.description: Set cutoff frequency in Hertz. Allowed range is 20000 to 192000. Default value is 20000.
options.name: cutoff

options.description: Set filter order. Available values are from 3 to 20. Default value is 10.
options.name: order

options.description: Set input gain level. Allowed range is from 0 to 1. Default value is 1.
options.name: level
